    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaf Blowing Simulator is a cozy co-op job simulator where you can blow away your worries with satisfying leaf physics. Whether solo or with a crew of fellow groundskeepers, fire up your leaf blower and blow away every leaf in sight. Can you find peace in the clutter of leaves?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/45149b4604675ba2bf25e1db8ee7f00b.poster.avif?t=1764604286\" width=960 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/45149b4604675ba2bf25e1db8ee7f00b.webm?t=1764604286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/45149b4604675ba2bf25e1db8ee7f00b.mp4?t=1764604286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WORK TOGETHER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teamwork makes the yard shine! You’ll have to coordinate with friends to master the art of yard clean-up. Help each other clear corners and roofs, or place ladders and fans to make it easier to clear the area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/60bb735c99fdd2bd61d692383100a696.poster.avif?t=1764604286\" width=960 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/60bb735c99fdd2bd61d692383100a696.webm?t=1764604286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/60bb735c99fdd2bd61d692383100a696.mp4?t=1764604286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BLOW THE STRESS AWAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn chores into charm! Blow leaves into tidy piles, chase the strays, and enjoy the soothing rhythm of a job well done. It’s the perfect way to unwind after a long day!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/15b96fbe9c5d73faadbeb24653345063.poster.avif?t=1764604286\" width=960 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/15b96fbe9c5d73faadbeb24653345063.webm?t=1764604286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/15b96fbe9c5d73faadbeb24653345063.mp4?t=1764604286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YARD WORK IS BETTER WITH FRIENDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax, unwind, and blow leaves with friends in Online Co-op! Work together to tidy each location, share equipment, and discover how much fun a simple task can be when it’s done together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/64a168ab7a24fdda10a00eac24ddcade.poster.avif?t=1764604286\" width=960 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/64a168ab7a24fdda10a00eac24ddcade.webm?t=1764604286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245210/extras/64a168ab7a24fdda10a00eac24ddcade.mp4?t=1764604286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blow leaves alone or with a total of 6 friends online</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cozy levels full of leaves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgradable leaf blowers and unlockable equipment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online co-op and offline single player</p></li></ul>",
